<p>&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 19.0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: x-small;">此时闲暇，不免收掇旧文，却见三秋故作。聊想昔年读之，如觉昨日，而今高墙深筑，虽有小聚，而难解心中孤苦。春秋轮转，又至五月，牡丹花盛极而衰，柳絮不扬，惠熙依然，然则光阴西逝，十九岁之我化羽升灵。细细斟酌老友字句，不免赧然，心病久矣，虽有弦歌相慰，然红尘深坠，竟难脱身。天边鸿雁传字，吾囿居人世，岂可逍遥，如何逍遥？</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: x-small;"><span style="line-height: 19.0px;">             <br>         </span></span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: x-small;"><span style="line-height: 19.0px;">             <br>         </span></span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">牡丹亭立夏</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">锦瑟暗度年华</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">白风白水白衣袷</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">蝴蝶晓梦无瑕</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">谁命中授你桃花</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">点厾膏肓里的朱砂</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">唯恋这，十二信风游丝软</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">莫敢闻，三千碛漠沙弹铗</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">云为鞍辔风为马</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">血染江山姽婳</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">诗中豪迈生涯</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">终抵不过茜纱窗下</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">点点爇烛泪</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">悠悠掌上花</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">谁揽年华为弓</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">十九载音尘去无踪。</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">水泻秋湍影相从</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">始知池下有游龙</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 10.0pt;">明眸净瞳，执笔剖开万物真容</span></p><p>    <span style="font-family: 宋体;font-si